name: Bo Shuda
Lore: 'In order to remain a successful crime lord, Jabba must ensure the safety of all those who seek to do business with him.',
Text: 'Deploy on Audience Chamber. If you have an alien here, no battles or Force drains may take place here and your aliens cannot be targeted by Trap Door. Effect canceled if opponent occupies this site without an alien. (Immune to Alter.)',
